StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETTUTORSTAFF
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETTUTORSTAFF(cTutorStaff OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cTutorStaff FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT TutorStaff_table.idPerson, TutorStaff_table.surname, TutorStaff_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; TutorStaff_table.title, TutorStaff_table.address, TutorStaff_table.phone, TutorStaff_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; TutorStaff_table.campusLocation, TutorStaff_table.idBuilding,TutorStaff_table.numberOffice,&lt;br/&gt; TutorStaff_table.staffType, TutorStaff_table.numberHours, TutorStaff_table.rate&lt;br/&gt; FROM TutorStaff_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getTutorStaff;
